text: Lindsay Davenport and Corina Morariu were the defending champions, but neither competed this year. Chanda Rubin and Sandrine Testud won the title by defeating Cara Black and Amy Frazier 6–4, 6–4 in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== * Official results archive (ITF) * Official results archive (WTA) Doubles Bank of the West Classic - Doubles
